match.name: December NRL22 @ Hobble Creek Utah
match.about:
Let's shoot! zero starts at 8:30, safety brief at 9:00. bring a friend!

With the range finishing the  back berm removal, we will be doing option 2!

Recommended Gear:

-Rifle
-Magazine
-Scope
-Bipod
-Ammo
-Support Bag

Optional Gear:

-Spotting Scope/Binoculars
-Ballistic Calculator
-Dope Card Holder

All gear can be found at www.nextshotprecision.com
